## Basic Example

```vx
api.setPlayerId<
    numberVariation=[1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8,9,0]
>;

if userFirstExperience{FE} => {
    setNumberVariants<>2;
}
```

This example creates a player identifier and applies Number Variant 2 when the user is detected as a first-time experience.

