## Standard Library

### VXPlayer

Player management utilities.

```vx
player = VXPlayer.create();
player.assignIdentity();
```

### VXNet

Networking and synchronization.

```vx
VXNet.connect<"server.vx">;
```

### VXUI

User interface generation.

```vx
panel = VXUI.createPanel<"Main Menu">;
```

